<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.7">
<l>ventiṟal kaḷiṟum vēlaivā yamutum</l>
<l>viṇṇoṭu viṇṇavark karacum</l>
<l>intiraṟ karuḷi yemakkumīn taruḷu</l>
<l>mentaiyem maṭikaḷem perumāṉ</l>
<l>antarat tamara raṭiyiṇai vaṇaṅka</l>
<l>vāyira mukattiṉā laruḷi</l>
<l>mantarat tiḻinta kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father, our god, our great lord who, having granted Indra</l>
<l rend="indent">a cruel, strong elephant, nectar from the sea,</l>
<l>And dominion over heaven and gods, graciously gives out [gifts] to us, too,</l>
<l>He is the one in Badarī Āśrama on the banks of the Ganges</l>
<l rend="indent">which descends [Mount] Mandara,</l>
<l>Graciously through a thousand head [waters], as immortals in heaven worship</l>
<l rend="indent">both of [his] feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
